rvention sera payée mensuellement et directement à votre établissement de crédit.</p><p>Le montant dépendra de :</p><ul><li>la perte de revenus réellement subie ;</li><li>votre amortissement mensuel ;</li><li>la durée de la période pendant laquelle vous faites appel à l’assurance.</li></ul><p>La prime ne peut jamais dépasser les 500 ou 600 euros par mois.</p></div></div>"},"naam":{"en":"Contribution","nl":"Financieel voordeel","en-x-generated":"<p>The amount you receive when you become unemployed or disabled depends on</p><ul><li>your loss of income</li><li>your monthly repayment</li><li>and the duration of unemployment or disability.</li></ul><p>The allowance amounts to:</p><ul><li><strong>a maximum of 500 euro</strong> per month</li><li>and <strong>exceptionally 600</strong> euros per month for people building a new home with an energy level lower than E70 and a taxable income below these income limits:<ul><li>51,840 euros for a single person</li><li>74,050 euros for legal or de facto cohabitants, to be increased by 4,150 euros per dependent person</li><li>74,050 euros for a single person with one dependant, to be increased by 4,150 euros per additional dependant.</li></ul></li></ul><p>The amount decreases the longer one receives an allowance.</p><h3>Payments</h3><p>The allowance is paid monthly directly to your credit institution.</p><p>You can get an allowance <strong>for a maximum of 36</strong> months. If there is an interruption in the period of unemployment or incapacity for work, the different periods are added up.</p><p>In case of <strong>involuntary unemployment</strong>, you are entitled to the allowances for a maximum of <strong>18 consecutive months</strong>. To qualify for a subsequent period of allowances, you must again have worked full-time or part-time for at least 3 months.</p><p>The end date of the insurance policy does not affect the period of relief. These are two separate terms. As long as the insurance term runs (maximum 10 years), you can apply for the allowance, but it is perfectly possible that you will still receive the monthly allowance when the end date of the policy has passed, as long as the conditions are met.</p>","fr":"Financieel voordeel","nl-BE-x-formal":"Financieel voordeel","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Financieel voordeel","de":"Financieel voordeel"},"@type":"FinancieelVoordeel","order":0}],"creatie":"2009-08-25T08:22:36Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2024-01-12T14:44:37Z","laatstOntvangen":"2024-06-18T17:25:32.356880361Z","productnummer":"185","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"en-x-generated":"<p>Flemish Housing Fund<br>Department of Insurance Guaranteed Housing<br>Ieperlaan 41<br>1000 Brussels</p><p>telephone: 02 548 92 39 (available every morning between 8.30 a.m. and 12 noon, except Thursday)<br>e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be\">vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be</a></p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","en":"See also on vlaanderen.be"},"url":"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/Product/4767a308-a18f-4533-8381-7cb1d99a755a"},"metadata":{"uJeVersie":"35.3.0","generatedFormeleFields":false,"generatedInformeleFields":true},"@id":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantiesnapshot/667a585c-d416-4712-84e8-afbbac22bc2a","@type":"InstantieSnapshot","isVersionOf":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantie/88f01834-aece-4d6a-a846-a7f67cd60ac7"},{"id":"4109ddba-02a6-4493-8ac4-dbb05e550317","generatedAtTime":"2024-06-18T17:25:31.772007Z","bevoegdBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"uitvoerendBestuursniveaus":["Derden"],"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"EPC Bouw","nl":"EPC Bouw","en":"EPC Construction ","nl-BE-x-formal":"EPC Bouw"},"beschrijving":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Bouwprojecten met een bouwaanvraag vanaf 2006 moeten aan de <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/energieprestatieregelgeving-voor-nieuwbouw-en-renovatie-epb\">EPB-regelgeving</a> voldoen. Na het indienen va